name: Special Occasion Custom Order ~ Classique Cloth Doll
description:
An opportunity to customise a Classique cloth doll. 

Customisation:-

Style ~ brights or soft romantic florals/pastels
Complexion ~ porcelain, ivory, caramel or tan 
Eyes ~ open or softly closed
Hair ~ white, red, pale pink, dark pink, caramel, brunette, black.
Hairstyle ~ single or double bun, pigtails

Please note your customised requests in the comments section upon checkout however please also feel free to contact our studio to discuss your order.
 
For fabric colourings, please choose approximately 2/3 shades in order of preference. Specific fabric choices may not be possible and will depend on stock levels. In the instance a particular fabric is not in stock, an alternative will be chosen.  If you do request the use of a specific fabric which requires ordering, a postal surcharge may apply.
